build /home/stone/dev/projects/articulate/GaussianArt/submodules/simple-knn/build/temp.linux-x86_64-3.10/spatial.o: cuda_compile /home/stone/dev/projects/articulate/GaussianArt/submodules/simple-knn/spatial.cu








